# Optional. If unset, the Spotify button is hidden and the app still works
# (Apple Music links and lyric matching don't need any auth).
#
# Get a Client ID from https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
#   1. Create an app
#   2. Add http://localhost:8081/ to its redirect URIs (and your deploy URL
#      later, e.g. https://yourdomain.com/)
#   3. Copy the Client ID below — there is no secret to set, this app uses
#      Authorization Code with PKCE.
EXPO_PUBLIC_SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=
